{"tid":807170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李登輝稱曾到訪中國 並停留數日","createTime":"2018-09-05T10:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:19:51.000Z","uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7148523f0320d7bde5ac79f4cbd60e9135714245","tid":807170,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"前總統李登輝日前表示，在中國尚未自由民主之前，不會拜訪中國。但他昨天透露，年輕時早已造訪過中國。在他十八、十九歲時，坐船前往日本留學，途中停留山東青島數日，對碼頭工人「山東大漢」印象深刻。<br />\n<br />\n李登輝昨天與媒體座談時，提起訪中往事。他少時乘船赴日，要到京都帝大留學，途中在青島休息四、五天，看到很多身材高大、臉黑黑的山東大漢；媒體追問，「當地小姐美嗎？」李則笑答，「沒看到小姐，只看到山東大漢。」<br />\n<br />\n颱風來襲，李登輝取消昨、今兩天雲林參訪行程，原本預計昨天至雲林科技大學的演講也取消，但數十名雲科大學生仍包車，赴李下塌飯店拜訪；李登輝在飯店內與學生座談，一個多小時演講全程站立。<br />\n<br />\n來自西安的趙姓陸生向李登輝提問，對陸生有何看法？李登輝說，希望有更多大陸人來台灣，看看有何不同；台灣是一個自由民主國家，「大陸嘴巴上努力，事實上沒有」。<br />\n<br />\n李登輝說，中國騙老百姓太多了，「過去的國民黨也是」，希望陸生來台灣，「看看李登輝寫什麼東西」，並多多學習，看看民主、自由，回去告訴同胞。<br />\n<br />\n李登輝送趙姓陸生一本他的簽名著作「最高領導者的條件」，還笑說：「這本書大陸沒有，很珍貴喔。」<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6131/218180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6131%2F218180&d=UacojdqbEYzd%2Fs7TQUlVLACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=78bea4b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6131/218180</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"3c1b739d2582da696b1c3a4f774184899a55dab7","tid":807170,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"根據某人邏輯去過中國就係投共<br />\n咁李登輝係咪投共？"},{"pid":"5e38def7edb2812f4062ca21777c04dcb3c5c1dc","tid":807170,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"佢仲話日本同咁污糟既民族打仗點可能贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc80802cae91e70fec21cfd9e601528b9a813ca5","tid":807170,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c1b739d2582da696b1c3a4f774184899a55dab7","tid":807170,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"根據某人邏輯去過中國就係投共<br />\n咁李登輝係咪投共？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"佢係日本人黎架<br />\n日治時期經日治山東去日本讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9062aa7826b05322346b9808e94bd94240e81b","tid":807170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.martinoei.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E6%9D%8E%E7%99%BB%E8%BC%9D-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.martinoei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25BC%259D-min.jpg&h=865a5fb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ffb994d6880d4993a64dcd272d5c15489ed7477","tid":807170,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3bab8928ab80d7d4e82d09d4dc99e55314f741c","tid":807170,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc80802cae91e70fec21cfd9e601528b9a813ca5","tid":807170,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c1b739d2582da696b1c3a4f774184899a55dab7","tid":807170,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"根據某人邏輯去過中國就係投共<br />\n咁李登輝係咪投共？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"佢係日本人黎架<br />\n日治時期經日治山東去日本讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/141438_2dae3998c0875abd4309135313442b38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F141438_2dae3998c0875abd4309135313442b38.png&h=07ecd7cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8750086ee67ff2bd08c2de2c2ac55b483fdd6bd0","tid":807170,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ffb994d6880d4993a64dcd272d5c15489ed7477","tid":807170,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:17:36.0